31#include "mech_locl.h"
32
33GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
34gss_unseal(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
35 gss_ctx_id_t context_handle,
36 gss_buffer_t input_message_buffer,
37 gss_buffer_t output_message_buffer,
38 int *conf_state,
39 int *qop_state)
40{
41
42 return (gss_unwrap(minor_status,
43 context_handle, input_message_buffer,
44 output_message_buffer, conf_state, (gss_qop_t *)qop_state));
45}
